<span id="freeTextContainer979784455026127815">WOW...what an amazing book! This book was gifted to me in exchange for an honest review. If you are looking for a book with an emotional rollercoaster ride, then you need to read this. Make sure to have tissues ready.<br/><br/>David loses his wife after an accident that they were involved in. He now has to figure out how to get through life without her and how to be a single dad to his two children. He meets Olivia through his sister Destiny who are both child therapists. She helps him work through some o</span>
  <span id="freeText979784455026127815" style="display:none">WOW...what an amazing book! This book was gifted to me in exchange for an honest review. If you are looking for a book with an emotional rollercoaster ride, then you need to read this. Make sure to have tissues ready.<br /><br />David loses his wife after an accident that they were involved in. He now has to figure out how to get through life without her and how to be a single dad to his two children. He meets Olivia through his sister Destiny who are both child therapists. She helps him work through some of the hard things he needs to face. She is also working with Destiny to help his daughter Clare. She also knows how he is feeling as she has experienced loss like that as well. Will they be able to find love together and will he be able to move forward for his children as well? You will have to read to find out as I am not going to give anything away. The characters are so likable and the plot flows really good. I couldn't put the book down.<br /><br />This was my first book by this author and it won't be my last. If I could give it more than 5 stars I definitely would. <br /><br /></span>
