<span id="freeTextContainer1192083288087117507">I received this ARC for an honest review.<br/><br/>What a total breathe of fresh air (plus tears) this book was. Gone are the typical romances, this book touches on so many issues that I&apos;m sure many readers will relate to. We have David a strong successful attorney whose life is torn apart with the death of his wife, leaving him to not only deal with her death but deal with raising his 7 year old daughter as well as his new born son! Insert Olivia, fire cracker of a women who makes David face a lot! The w</span>
  <span id="freeText1192083288087117507" style="display:none">I received this ARC for an honest review.<br /><br />What a total breathe of fresh air (plus tears) this book was. Gone are the typical romances, this book touches on so many issues that I'm sure many readers will relate to. We have David a strong successful attorney whose life is torn apart with the death of his wife, leaving him to not only deal with her death but deal with raising his 7 year old daughter as well as his new born son! Insert Olivia, fire cracker of a women who makes David face a lot! The writing was perfect, everything flowed so well but not just that we are taken on a journey through David and Olivia's POVs. I many not of ever dealt with the pain these characters faced but I felt I was there with them feeling their every emotion. Well done, as I have never been on a journey like this ever from a book. I look forward to reading more from this author!</span>
