        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1372769554" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7417152068626206638">Wow just finished this and what an amazingly emotional read. <br/><br/>This was the first book that I&apos;ve read from Torrie Robles so I had no expectations but I was blown away by this read. <br/><br/>To be honest, it started a little slow and I wasn&apos;t sure if I was going to like it, but then before I knew it, I was sucked right in and I couldn&apos;t get through it quick enough.<br/><br/>Love After Pain, is simply a beautifully written love story of two people coming together for a second chance at love. It really tugged at the he</span>
  <span id="freeText7417152068626206638" style="display:none">Wow just finished this and what an amazingly emotional read. <br /><br />This was the first book that I've read from Torrie Robles so I had no expectations but I was blown away by this read. <br /><br />To be honest, it started a little slow and I wasn't sure if I was going to like it, but then before I knew it, I was sucked right in and I couldn't get through it quick enough.<br /><br />Love After Pain, is simply a beautifully written love story of two people coming together for a second chance at love. It really tugged at the heartstrings and I dare anyone to get through it without shedding a tear. <br /><br />I would heartily recommend this book.<br /><br />I was gifted a copy of this book in exchange for an honest review.</span>
