          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/25657858-love-after-pain">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1373925909" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15717453928071906032">What a great book. David just lost his wife and is left not only to deal with his grief but to raise his seven year old daughter and his newborn son. With the support of his family, he begins going through the motions of life. Will he open himself up to life and love again, or is he totally closed off because of the loss of the &quot;love of his life&quot;.<br/>Torrie Robles does a great job with character development. Every character has depth and purpose. Well worth the time to read. This is the first book I</span>
  <span id="freeText15717453928071906032" style="display:none">What a great book. David just lost his wife and is left not only to deal with his grief but to raise his seven year old daughter and his newborn son. With the support of his family, he begins going through the motions of life. Will he open himself up to life and love again, or is he totally closed off because of the loss of the "love of his life".<br />Torrie Robles does a great job with character development. Every character has depth and purpose. Well worth the time to read. This is the first book I have read by this author, and if this is any indication of her creativity and dedication to telling a great story, I look forward to reading more by this author.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15717453928071906032" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
